üìå Project Name: FixNow

A mobile-first platform connecting users with certified local technicians (mechanics, plumbers, electricians, etc.) for fast, reliable service.

-------------------------------------------------------------------
‚≠ê 1. SYSTEM OVERVIEW
FixNow is a two-sided marketplace with:
Users requesting repair services
Technicians offering services
Admin panel to manage the platform

Modes:
On-demand technician request
Scheduled bookings
Payment inside the app (M-Pesa + card)

-------------------------------------------------------------------
‚≠ê 2. USER FLOW (For Flowchart generation)
Start ‚Üí User opens app ‚Üí Login/Sign Up ‚Üí Browse services ‚Üí Select technician or auto-match ‚Üí View pricing ‚Üí Book service ‚Üí Technician accepts ‚Üí Technician travels to user ‚Üí Work completed ‚Üí User pays ‚Üí User rates technician ‚Üí End

-------------------------------------------------------------------
‚≠ê 3. TECHNICIAN FLOW
Start ‚Üí Technician registers ‚Üí Submit documents ‚Üí Admin verification ‚Üí Technician online/offline toggle ‚Üí Receives job ‚Üí Accept job ‚Üí Travel to location ‚Üí Complete task ‚Üí Mark job done ‚Üí Receive payment ‚Üí End

-------------------------------------------------------------------
‚≠ê 4. CORE FEATURES
